    <item>
      <title>09/18/2010 - Libertarian Generalizations</title>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Sep 2010 19:00:00 -0700</pubDate>
      <itunes:author>Nick Coons, Richard Sutton, and Jim Iannuzo</itunes:author>
      <itunes:summary>On this evening's show, we discussed a video on YouTube titled Why I Hate Libertarians.&amp;nbsp; We felt it was important to discuss this video, not because it had anything relevant to say about libertarianism (it didn't), nor that it struck a chord with rational thinkers (it didn't), nor that it even threatened the ideological movement libertarians pursue (it didn't).&amp;nbsp; What it did was represent libertarians as mindless cult members, which any reasonable person can see through, including the hypocrisy within the first 30 seconds.
We invited the creator of this video to come on the show so we could discuss his positions, but he beligerantly declined.</itunes:summary>
