      <itunes:author>Nick Coons, Richard Sutton, and Jim Iannuzo</itunes:author>
      <itunes:summary>Welcome to the White House, President Obama.&amp;nbsp; There seem to be three types of people with regards to our new President.&amp;nbsp; The first is hopeful of the change he talks about, the second is fearful of the change, and the third believe that there won't actually be any change.&amp;nbsp; We at the Libertarian Solution fall into the last category.&amp;nbsp; While there will be superficial modifications, the overall trend of bigger and more intrusive government will stay the course, so to speak.</itunes:summary>
